data.description: Great home located in Grove Lakes subdivision  This charming brick home nestled in the heart of an established subdivision. This delightful property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a separate dining room, and a sunroom, offering ample space for comfortable living and entertaining.    A welcoming front porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or watching the sunset. Step inside to discover a spacious living area, ideal for relaxation and gatherings.    The bedrooms are generously sized, offering a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The kitchen bright and equipped with modern appliances for you and your family to enjoy.    Outside, the property includes a two-car carport, providing convenient parking and additional storage space. The backyard offers a private oasis, the fenced in area is perfect for outdoor activities and enjoying the fresh air.    Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise.
